# MasterControl (mascon)

Minimal personal CLI console for WSL-oriented workflows.

## Install

```bash
cd /path/to/mascon
python3 -m pip install -e .
```

## First-time config

```bash
mkdir -p ~/.config/mascon
cat > ~/.config/mascon/config.toml <<'TOML'
profile = "apiron"
mode = "work"
workspace = "~/workspace"
default_aws_profile = "dev"

[jumps]
workspace = "~/workspace"
mastercontrol = "~/workspace/mastercontrol"
sophia = "~/workspace/sophia-core"
vault = "~/workspace/virtual-vault"
TOML
```

## Usage

```bash
mascon start
mascon repo check
mascon repo ship -m "feat: add dashboard"
mascon aws whoami
mascon path win . --copy
mascon open .
mascon jump workspace
```
